'''Dhumbudya''': aya [[zvipembenene]] zvinodyiwa uye zvakafanana ne[[mhashu]] asi zvakatitsongei zviri zwidiki uyewo zviine muviri uneruvara rwepfumbi rwakafanana nemashizha emiti. Zvinonyanya kuonekwa munguva yokunaya kwemvura. Madhumbudya anobhururukawo semhashu. Madhumbudya, kana abikwa, ane mafuta akawanda kudarika mhashu. Nokuda kwekuva nemafuta akawanda, madhumbudya anozivikamwa neshoko rokuti [[dzambarafuta]] kana kuti [[tambarafuta]].
